file1.highlighted_code: import math def fac_sum_split_num(n): old_num = n ans = 0 while n > 0: ans += math.factorial(n % 10) n //= 10 if ans == old_num: return('Yes') else: return('No') t = int(input()) for _ in range(t): num = int(input()) print(fac_sum_split_num(num))
